external_knowledge:
- 'Last login times' refers to the most recent 'attempted_at' timestamp in the 'login_attempts' table for each user; 
- 'Last session creation times' refers to the most recent 'created_at' timestamp in the 'user_sessions' table for each user; 
- 'Last password reset requests' refers to the most recent 'requested_at' timestamp in the 'password_resets' table for each user, with requests made after '2023-07-01' being considered; 
- 'Dark mode preferences' refers to the 'setting_value' of the 'dark_mode' setting in the 'settings' table under the 'theme' category for each user.
